column5: I have reservations planned for the 2nd week in july at goose bay on lac seul. I was wondering if anyone could tell me productive methods for location and presentation. also this is my first time to goose bay and i'd some opinions on how they operate there business.Thanks,JOE
There was much discussion on this resort. Do a search using "Goose Bay" and you find a couple threads on the subject. Or just go back to page 7 or 8 and you will find it.
